# .vercelignore — 3C Word Search
# Vercel should ONLY deploy /api folder for OAuth
# All other content is hosted on GitHub Pages

# Ignore everything except /api
/*
!/api

# Ignore all static content directories
admin/
public/
js/
static/

# Ignore static files
*.html
*.css
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.md

# Keep API folder
!api/**
